#SYMBOL_NAME "AVWorkz Analog to Serial v1.0"
#HINT "Simple module to convert analog to serial, equivalent to ITOA"
#DEFAULT_VOLATILE
#ENABLE_STACK_CHECKING

#HELP_BEGIN

This module basically takes in an analog input and sends it out as string (ITOA). 


